/**
 * Critical-path styles
 *
 * These styles are inserted directly into the <head> using a <style> tag. This
 * means the portion of the page that is visible on pageload can be rendered
 * before the browser has received the stylesheet in a subsequent request.
 *
 * Since the loading overlay shows on pageload, we can simply just use the
 * overlay styles for the critical-path.
 */
/*=========
